abstract: Follow along for live updates and analysis from Game 4 of the World Series.
snippet: Follow along for live updates and analysis from Game 4 of the World Series.
lead_paragraph: ARLINGTON, Tex. - With his team in need of a win and his bullpen in need of some rest, the Rangers' Derek Holland rose to the occasion, allowing just two hits over eight and a third innings as the Rangers beat the Cardinals, 4-0, to tie the World Series at two games apiece.
